          Emergency Roadside Assistance up to $100 per occurrence.
          This includes towing, fuel delivery, and battery services.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <section class="header">
          <i class="fa fa-motorcycle fa-2x"></i>
          <h3>Coverage</h3>
        </section>
        <p>
          CornerStone United, Inc. Extended Protection Program is a
          comprehensive plan that covers all major components, parts and
          electrical/computer systems along with all seals, gaskets and
          shocks on our motorcycle. Only normal wear or maintenance items
          are not covered. We've built the CornerStone United, Inc. Extended
          Protection Program around coverage, not exclusions.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <section class="header">
          <i class="fa fa-map-signs fa-2x"></i>
          <h3>Transferable</h3>
        </section>
        <p>
          CornerStone United, Inc. Extended Protection Program is transferable
          one time during the life of the plan to the next owner, increasing
          your motorcycle's resale value. The contract can also be cancelled
          for a refund in the event of an accident or sale.
        </p>
